{"tid":788185,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[神人]古天樂第100所希望小學建成 網友曝新學期將投入使用 第105間已經奠基","createTime":"2018-08-21T09:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T10:29:18.000Z","uid":48083,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"02cd3f40f8c5f29cb83a0501397493285b6a57fc","tid":788185,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T09:28:45.000Z","msg":"　　古天樂努力做公益的形象，被更多人知道，他卻素來相當低調，也一直在行動。上個月，古天樂在廣西梧州捐建的第99所希望小學舉辦了竣工典禮，昨天，又有網友爆料古天樂第100教學樓已經建成。<br />\n<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/4411868084/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F4411868084%2F0&h=072d8b18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　爆料的網友發視頻稱&ldquo;新學校，孩子們下學期就要入學了。&rdquo;從畫面來看，樓上掛著&ldquo;古天樂第100教學樓&rdquo;的字樣，樓層嶄新而且打掃得很乾淨。<br />\n<br />\n　　網友紛紛為古天樂點讚，有網友調侃說：&ldquo;古天樂真的不行，兩面三刀，表面上什麼都沒有，背地裡偷偷蓋學校。&rdquo;還有網友稱&ldquo;古天樂，加油&rdquo;。<br />\n<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/4411874140/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F4411874140%2F0&h=9e403bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/4411875340/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F4411875340%2F0&h=cb1e28f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　不得不說，古天樂太低調了。他默默做公益，捐建了100所希望小學，卻幾乎沒有公開宣傳。有媒體曾想採訪古天樂，他通過經紀人回應，&ldquo;只是本著做慈善的心，不想講錢，也沒有目標要捐建多少學校。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n(第99間)<br />\n<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/3972434892/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F3972434892%2F0&h=5561a0ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/4411886663/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F4411886663%2F0&h=5a73225b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/1829117563/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F1829117563%2F0&h=e66b1122&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　現在，第100教學樓已經建成，新學期就可以投入使用了。而之前，也有網友爆料&ldquo;田蓬鎮中心小學古天樂第105綜合樓奠基儀式&rdquo;舉行，也就是說，古天樂捐建學校的公益行動一直在路上，在繼續。<br />\n<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/4338716139/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F4338716139%2F0&h=54c0dd95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/1829113127/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F1829113127%2F0&h=501328d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　作為演員，古天樂顏值、演技&ldquo;雙一流&rdquo;，是娛樂圈不可多得的偶像實力派，而作為慈善家，他踏實、低調，為許許多多貧困地區的孩子讀書求學打造良好環境。為這樣的偶像點讚！ （本文係土酷工作室作者&ldquo;王團&rdquo;原創出品，謝絕轉載）<br />\n<br />\nTHE END<br />\n<a href=\"https://new.qq.com/omn/20180717/20180717A0HA1T.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnew.qq.com%2Fomn%2F20180717%2F20180717A0HA1T.html&d=eLc2k4X4fye4VeyyALA54AHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=d877fdf2\" target=\"_blank\">https://new.qq.com/omn/20180717/20180717A0HA1T.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0268f45c3cccb372e316a23033bf620d2f591c15","tid":788185,"uid":7374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"古神"},{"pid":"c27edf99dcab47c5642976d0c1f0d68b282eb6bc","tid":788185,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass